snippet.title: Touhou Mystia's Izakaya Collab Announced!! [Touhou Danmaku Kagura Phantasia Lost]
snippet.description:
The collaboration between "Touhou Mystia's Izakaya" and "Touhou Danmaku Kagura Phantasia Lost" has just been announced!
Please look forward to further news~!!

"Touhou Danmaku Kagura Phantasia Lost" will finally be released on Steam, on February 8, 2024!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2190220/_/


_____
Presented by Unknown X

○Touhou Danmaku Kagura Phantasia Lost - Official website
https://danmaku.jp/phantasia-lost/en/

○Touhou Danmaku Kagura - Official Twitter
https://twitter.com/danmakujp
